Update procedure:

[1] Modify changelog as appropriate.
[2] Gather debian/ directory into a littleutils_1.0.x-y.debian.tar.gz tarball.

Build procedure:

[1] Copy main source tarball to CWD as littleutils_1.0.x.orig.tar.lzma.
[2] Unpack littleutils_1.0.x.orig.tar.lzma.
[3] Change to littleutils_1.0.x directory.
[4] Unpack littleutils_1.0.x-y.debian.tar.gz tarball.
[5] Run dpkg-buildpackage command.  Use -uc and -us options until signatures are established.
